r, along with a treasure trove of unforgettable memories.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Now answer me this... What drives you to venture on this risky journey?\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"What about you, brave adventurer? Do you seek riches or fame? Baa.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Thus you shall accompany the merchants and travel across the high seas to Rinascita.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"They say treasures fill its lands, and you'll gain a fortune beyond your wildest dreams!","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"It appears you're already quite renowned! Baa. Just traverse countless lands along the boundless horizon, and all shall know your name!","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"If you desire neither wealth nor honor, why do you choose to venture to the Gateway of Wishes?\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Very well... then believe in my tale, and close your eyes, Little Warrior and her companions.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"When you open your eyes, a brand-new adventure shall unfold before you.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Once we've completed this story together, your wishes will all be granted!","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036}]}